  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Arya X</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> chapter</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_storm_of_swords\" title=\"A storm of swords\"><img alt=\"AStormOfSwords.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg/220px-AStormOfSwords.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"353\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"/images/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg 1.5x\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">POV</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">Riverlands</a>, close to <a href=\"/index.php/The_Twins\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Twins\">the Twins</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Page</th><td>\n568 <small>UK HC</small> <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters_Table_of_contents\" title=\"Chapters Table of contents\">Other versions</a>)</small></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Chapter chronology <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters\" title=\"Chapters\">All</a>)</small></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_47\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 47\">Arya IX</a><br />↑</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_49\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 49\">Catelyn VI</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">&#160;←</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; padding-right:0.1em; padding-left:0.1em;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Arya X</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">→&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_51\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 51\">Catelyn VII</a></td>\n</tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n↓<br /><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_52\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 52\">Arya XI</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Synopsis\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Synopsis</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Character_list\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character list</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Places_and_terms_mentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Places and terms mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References_and_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References and Notes</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Synopsis\">Synopsis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_50&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Synopsis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Sandor_Clegane\" title=\"Sandor Clegane\">Sandor</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya</a> arrive at <a href=\"/index.php/The_Twins\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Twins\">the Twins</a> where Sandor hopes to ransom Arya to <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">her family</a>. To get there The Hound had robbed a farmer of his <a href=\"/index.php/Wagon\" title=\"Wagon\">wagon</a> and casks to disguise themselves as simple farmers who have come to bring pork to the feast. The castle is closed so they are sent to the pavilions instead where the common soldiers are. Arya recognizes a few coats of arms but there is nobody she knows. The soldiers drink to the health of Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Westerling\" title=\"Jeyne Westerling\">Jeyne</a> whose name is unfamiliar to Arya. As Sandor wants to ransom Arya they head to the castle. \n</p><p><br />\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character_list\">Character list</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_50&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character list\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:3; column-width:300px;\"> \n<p><b>Appearing:</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Sandor_Clegane\" title=\"Sandor Clegane\">Sandor Clegane</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Donnel_Haigh\" title=\"Donnel Haigh\">Donnel Haigh</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>Mentioned:</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Wyman_Manderly\" title=\"Wyman Manderly\">Wyman Manderly</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Edmure_Tully\" title=\"Edmure Tully\">Edmure Tully</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Shella_Whent\" title=\"Shella Whent\">Shella Whent</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a></l